WEBVTT

1
00:06:03.490 --> 00:06:05.090 
跟帮派没有关系是吗
at the bus stop was not gang affiliated?

2
00:06:05.090 --> 00:06:07.420 
是的  长官  保罗·霍勒  高四学生
That is correct, sir. Paul Haller, high school senior.

3
00:06:07.420 --> 00:06:08.540 
但也不是什么好鸟
Not an angel, though.

4
00:06:08.540 --> 00:06:12.220 
霍勒曾因几次小偷小摸被逮捕过
Haller has a few minor robbery arrests from the past,

5
00:06:12.220 --> 00:06:14.750 
警方在他身上发现了一个钱包
and police found a wallet on his body,

6
00:06:14.760 --> 00:06:17.790 
现金和信用卡都属于一个叫西塔·帕特尔的人
cash and credit cards belonging to a Sita Patel.

7
00:06:17.790 --> 00:06:18.950 
抢钱包
Purse-snatching?

8
00:06:18.950 --> 00:06:20.070 
黑帮分子  抢劫犯
Gang members, mugger.

9
00:06:20.070 --> 00:06:21.670 
这可能是义务警员所为
We might be looking at a vigilante.

10
00:06:21.670 --> 00:06:23.450 
我刚跟克利夫兰警方通过电话
All right, I just got off the phone with Cleveland P.D.

11
00:06:23.450 --> 00:06:24.850 
如果我们面对的是杀人狂
If we are dealing with a spree killer,

12
00:06:24.850 --> 00:06:26.310 
至少他现在还能自控
at least he's on a slower boil now.

13
00:06:26.310 --> 00:06:28.140 
过去几个小时没有犯下新的案子
No new incidents reported in the past hour.

14
00:06:28.150 --> 00:06:30.730 
加油站的死者不仅中了枪
The victim at the gas station wasn't just shot.

15
00:06:30.740 --> 00:06:33.160 
尸体表明他被一辆大车
The body showed signs of having been run over multiple times

